  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Construction Manager",
  "description": "<ul><li>Overseeing and directing projects to completion stage.</li><li>Ensure projects are completed within the expected time, cost & quality .</li><li>Coordinate with relevant parties to manage progress of the project to ensure effective project delivery.</li><li>Lead team to manage project operations, schedule and specifications.</li><li>Manage operational cost to keep cost within the budget.</li><li>Manage subcontractors’ activities to ensure compliance of contract requirements.</li><li>Monitor compliance of work with the workplace safety and health regulations.</li><li>Monitor quality of project delivery to make sure they meet project requirements and regulations.</li><li>Plan and organize daily and weekly manpower or resources allocation to ensure smooth day to day site operation.</li><li>To coordinate with site supervisors, workers, vendors, sub-contractors to ensure projects are completed according to specifications, quality standards, cost and time frame.</li><li>Attend site kick off and weekly progress meetings or any ad-hoc meetings when required.</li><li>Responsible for manpower and progress reporting on daily & weekly basis.</li><li>Supervise daily site activities</li></ul>",
